description:
The best quality pencil polished tempered glass in the industry at great prices. Create your own beautiful Free Standing Display. You can design your own unit easily by using our connectors and tempered glass from our standard size list. Assembly is easy and quick with a flat head screwdriver. The hinge, hasp and combo lock create a convenient locking case worthy of your retail store's finest collectibles. Our connectors are designed for 3/16" thick tempered glass. Use on non-tempered glass is hazardous and may be a violation of building and safety codes.

description:
Universal "T" Concealed Standard
For moderate loads. 1/2" slots, 1 in on center for 1" adjustments. 
    The American Retail Supply UNIVERSAL SYSTEM is produced in accordance with major U.S. manufacturers' standards with regard to steal hardness and wall thickness. Some imported lines may not meet these exacting standards. This system is compatible with Capitol, Crown, Garcy, and Reeve. 
Standards 6'+ will be shipped VIA common carrier. Freight will be quoted separately. You will be notified of the freight amount.
